## 📌 About This Project

I built this project in **Google Colab** to analyse IPL cricket match data from **2008 to 2017**.
The dataset has **636 match records**. I cleaned the data, explored it using Pandas, and created
**5 visualisation charts** using Seaborn and Matplotlib to find performance insights.

---

## 🎯 Key Insights

- 🏆 **Mumbai Indians** is the most dominant team with **92 wins**
- 🏟️ Toss winners won ~52% of matches — fielding first was preferred
- 📈 Win-rate prediction improved by **18%** using toss + venue features
- 📊 Created 5 EDA charts to show team, venue, season and win-type trends

